init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is the story of the survivors of the first wave of the invasion, and how they begin to use their newfound abilities to fight back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The series was collected into a single volume:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Zora Chronicles was nominated for the Eisner Award for Best Limited Series in 2010.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Zora Chronicles was also nominated for the Harvey Award for Best New Series in 2010.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Zora Chronicles has been optioned for a film by the production company, The Gotham Group.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a huge fan of the Zora Chronicles and has read all of the books.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Mike asks Johnny to come to the set of the film for a special role.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Johnny is so excited that he can't wait to tell his friends.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In fact, they are downright jealous.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Johnny's friends are all big fans of the Zora Chronicles, too.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But they are upset that Johnny got the role instead of them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They don't want to see Johnny succeed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is determined to make the most of his opportunity.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But will Johnny's friends sabotage his big chance?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He explains that Johnny will be playing a young boy named Johnny who is a huge fan of the Zora Chronicles.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He can't wait to see himself on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But Johnny's excitement quickly turns to horror when he learns that his friends have followed him to the set.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are determined to ruin Johnny's big break.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are going to do everything they can to make sure Johnny's performance is a disaster.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But Johnny is determined to prove his friends wrong.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is going to give the best performance of his life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is going to focus on his performance and nothing else.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Johnny's friends are furious that Johnny is ignoring them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Johnny forgave them and they became friends again.
